Package: ovltools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for estimating distribution overlap between two sample distributions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Seongyong Park
Maintainer: Seongyong Park <psychemistz@gmail.com>
Description: ovltools provides some of known tools for estimating distribution overlap between two sample distributions.  
    It provides KNN, KDE, Histogram, Distribution fitting based distribution overlap calculation and 
    permutation test based signifiance testing. User can utilize this package for any perpose. 
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    FNN,
    fitdistrplus
Suggests:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
